one.description: Developed with ReactJS for the Front-End and HonoJS with edge workers for the Back-End. While it does not allow real purchases, the application will keep you up to date with the latest computer and electronics products. The catalog is automatically updated weekly.

two.description: Command-line media player written in NodeJS that supports content playback using various strategies. The application allows users to search and play music from YouTube (either playlists or via a URL) without the need to use a web browser.
